      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "The peace you seek is not found in a new map, but in the quiet realization that you don't need one anymore. You are not a passenger; you are the owner of this moment, and you have the right to step off the train and stay still. Letting go of the map is the bravest journey of all, because it means you finally belong to where you are.",
